thread.title: Cookie Tye

author: Cookie Tye
title: Cookie Tye
text: It is great that they always have sales and their shoes are so reasonably priced for the quality! Perfect for what I need because I have a shoe problem. Love shoes!! I just love that they constantly have different updated styles that they carry! I can scroll through all of their pages for hours at a time in search of the perfect shoes. I always purchase more than one when I get on the site. Don't know if that's a good thing or a bad thing LOL
